{"tid":1175292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地成日笑catgirl 其實佢好值得你地妒忌","createTime":"2019-05-28T12:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:20:51.000Z","uid":253512,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5868270379789544c563fe776c507911d356ae5","tid":1175292,"uid":253512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"你地笑佢肥+樣衰 外表差<br />\n但正正係咁 睇得出呀Ken唔係貪佢既外表<br />\n而家鐘意佢呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論佢變到幾肥 幾豬 幾醜 對波跌到低過條腰都好<br />\n呀Ken都對佢從一而終<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁先係真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試問有幾多人可以即使自己變到catgirl咁你既另一半都唔會離你而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你另一半呢一刻同你講唔會 <br />\n到最後如果你真係變成咁佢一定走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀Ken仲要承受住身邊人既閒言閒語<br />\n你地又笑佢catgirl坐一坐蓮唔止斷鳩連腰都斷鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢都甘願承受 睇得出佢一定好愛catgirl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀Ken先係真男人 Catgirl係好幸福既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主我都好想有一個可以無論佢變肥變醜都唔會離開佢既另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3980d077c257d3949e7fe2f91fc28e7e1c1331c","tid":1175292,"uid":253512,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"但講還講唔好係我個post貼相唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9d3d3a176e691456c8f3098f472c5486f0a686","tid":1175292,"uid":253512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji